        "text_EDYArr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": false,
            "text": "<h3>From the Heart...</h3><p>Hi, I’m <strong>Moira</strong>. For as long as I can remember, I have loved helping women find clothes that make them feel comfortable, confident, and beautifully themselves.</p><p>When my granddaughter <strong>Eileen</strong> came into my life, she brought a softness and joy that became the heart of this boutique. <strong>Moira & Eileen Boutique</strong> is more than a name. It is a small family story.</p><p>Every piece we choose is selected for real women and real life. Soft fabrics, flattering fits, and timeless styles made to feel easy and elegant.</p><p>This past year has not been easy for small boutiques like ours. It made us pause, reflect, and prepare for a fresh chapter.</p><p>That is why we have launched our <strong>Revival Sale</strong>. A chance to clear selected favourites, create space for what comes next, and continue this story with care.</p><p>Right now, every order truly matters.</p><p>Thank you for supporting a family-run boutique and helping us write our next chapter.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
